{"tid":25594,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[西歐］5月頭去14日西葡 求意見","createTime":"2016-12-06T08:20:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-15T12:27:40.000Z","uid":57774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9c4a975c6825f38012a6b3151911eff12fa1a4bc","tid":25594,"uid":57774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T08:20:11.000Z","msg":"5月頭會同女朋友去西葡14日, 想大家比下意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我同女朋友都唔睇波, 所以未必一定要去球場朝聖<br />\n都唔想去shopping<br />\n主要想睇下建築, 去下沙灘 飲下酒 relax<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nHKG &gt; Barcelona (2-3 day) &gt; Madrid (2 day) &gt; Segovia (day trip) &gt; Toledo (1 day)&gt; Cordoba (2 day) &gt; Sevilla (2 day) &gt; Lisbon + Porto (2 day) &gt; HKG<br />\n<br />\n大約呢個plan有無咩意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nGibraltar係咪最好搵時間去?<br />\nThanks<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a70e8b5facff04124a7fac2e9a85c6e5eca5a146","tid":25594,"uid":57774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T09:51:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62ef536b237c6a2e5f65a1c7a07880ee25c43823","tid":25594,"uid":9941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T09:53:42.000Z","msg":"屌仲諗緊咩葡萄牙西面"},{"pid":"ab52021846880da2474e2a47e1fd0e303ee57778","tid":25594,"uid":39733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T10:20:00.000Z","msg":"Lisbon + Porto 兩日？<br />\n全部時間攞晒嚟揸車/搭車？<br />\n<br />\nSkip 咗呢兩個地方，上 Granada 好過"},{"pid":"3aeff789e9cfbb460ccb80b3130b81903b4c6709","tid":25594,"uid":57774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T11:53:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Lisbon + Porto 兩日？<br />\n全部時間攞晒嚟揸車/搭車？<br />\n<br />\nSkip 咗呢兩個地方，上 Granada 好過</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁淨係Lisbon 兩日？我主要心態係去開就順手去埋😂"},{"pid":"a9503f2d3a728ef26e9230110bb180abfb896bd3","tid":25594,"uid":11976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T11:58:20.000Z","msg":"建議cordoba 唔洗用兩日<br />\n西維爾去cordoba 都係兩個鐘<br />\n可以選擇一日遊<br />\n另外你去得西班牙南面就建議俾兩日去Granada <br />\n相信你會睇得好開心"},{"pid":"c5bb23170e94550f52b59b4cdd02e7ff1a5b2f98","tid":25594,"uid":57774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T12:43:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>建議cordoba 唔洗用兩日<br />\n西維爾去cordoba 都係兩個鐘<br />\n可以選擇一日遊<br />\n另外你去得西班牙南面就建議俾兩日去Granada <br />\n相信你會睇得好開心</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好 再睇睇先 因為見書好少講Granada <br />\n多謝樓上兩位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac97a38954f306fbcfea5868e2398f4e35e8703b","tid":25594,"uid":11976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T13:21:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>建議cordoba 唔洗用兩日<br />\n西維爾去cordoba 都係兩個鐘<br />\n可以選擇一日遊<br />\n另外你去得西班牙南面就建議俾兩日去Granada <br />\n相信你會睇得好開心</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好 再睇睇先 因為見書好少講Granada <br />\n多謝樓上兩位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你試下search Alhambra 同albazin <br />\n去巴塞唔睇波試下睇opera <br />\n個theater 好出名好靚"},{"pid":"fde1b02367c5cdd5f735dfe2c38835dfd1b7125f","tid":25594,"uid":5477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T13:29:13.000Z","msg":"我個人鍾意hea遊 <br />\nLisbon Porto 節奏好舒服<br />\n我上年去兩個城市玩左7日都唔覺多"},{"pid":"aa5c1c335d95176fce296b207fea8d0584f67363","tid":25594,"uid":39733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T13:41:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我個人鍾意hea遊 <br />\n<br />\nLisbon Porto 節奏好舒服<br />\n<br />\n我上年去兩個城市玩左7日都唔覺多</blockquote><br />\nLisbon 加埋 Sintra 已經最少要三四日<br />\n睇完佢個 itinerary，真係應該 skip 咗葡萄牙"},{"pid":"6126d1dfa551ceaef3bbeb172a9742231211992e","tid":25594,"uid":27849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T16:00:32.000Z","msg":"3月尾去左22日，地方類似<br />\nValencia -&gt; Madrid -&gt; Granada -&gt; Gibraltar -&gt; Seville -&gt; Lagos -&gt; Lisbon -&gt; Porto -&gt; Barcelona <br />\n<br />\nValencia 如果唔係撞正la falles可skip<br />\nToledo我係住Madrid, day trip去：Madrid市內我覺得麻麻好睇，反而seville啲景點幾靚！plaza de espana好好j<br />\n極力推薦Granada, 記得要事先book定皇宮門飛，如果唔係，要朝早四、五點去排隊先可能買到飛<br />\nGibraltar一日行晒，幾特別，但冇時間都可以skip既。不過比我，都係會想吱一日時間去<br />\n<br />\nPorto同lisbon我都好鐘意！各自住左2晚定3晚，係Lisbon 一定要留一日時間去sintra同Cabo da Roca<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e33662722e149deaf53f80e8248d6c179987bf9","tid":25594,"uid":57774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T13:47:18.000Z","msg":"唔該哂上面幾位先<br />\nUpdate左 total 16 days 連飛機<br />\n9:00 arrive Barcelona total 4日&gt; 第四晚night bus to Madrid &gt; Madrid 1day + 2 days for Segovia Toledo day trip &gt; Cordoba 1day &gt; Granada 1day&gt; nerja 1day &gt; Sevilla 3 day 第3晚night bus to Lisbon&gt; 3 days Lisbon 包埋 Sinatra + Cabo da roca&gt; 第三日1430飛<br />\n<br />\n中間幾個city淨係stay1日睇落好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  但想去哂cordoba Granada nerja<br />\n如果要去上面三個地方，Malaga 迫住經過 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n定係應該唔好咁貪心<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無乜機會會去到歐洲<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f4d1d52ab4e4de60907e4961bbbe9e3a07d4cf5","tid":25594,"uid":57774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T10:06:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfd50e98a8ae53ce475e0ce68c7052d5e5e90833","tid":25594,"uid":27849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T12:15:08.000Z","msg":"一日真心好chur，會攰到冇心機玩<br />\n同埋Granada一日行唔晒，除非你朝早到，第二日夜晚走（我好似係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n記得book Alhambra tickets!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9060ba2467125e0fc0dd8e6fb87c524666b3f69","tid":25594,"uid":57774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T13:02:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一日真心好chur，會攰到冇心機玩<br />\n同埋Granada一日行唔晒，除非你朝早到，第二日夜晚走（我好似係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n記得book Alhambra tickets!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一定會book<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家就係諗住去少一日巴塞 再分下d travelling time 睇下會唔會鬆動d<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8611eb860e014c80c2d3240d886d64949759e056","tid":25594,"uid":8934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T13:52:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔該哂上面幾位先<br />\nUpdate左 total 16 days 連飛機<br />\n9:00 arrive Barcelona total 4日&amp;gt; 第四晚night bus to Madrid &amp;gt; Madrid 1day + 2 days for Segovia Toledo day trip &amp;gt; Cordoba 1day &amp;gt; Granada 1day&amp;gt; nerja 1day &amp;gt; Sevilla 3 day 第3晚night bus to Lisbon&amp;gt; 3 days Lisbon 包埋 Sinatra + Cabo da roca&amp;gt; 第三日1430飛<br />\n<br />\n中間幾個city淨係stay1日睇落好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  但想去哂cordoba Granada nerja<br />\n如果要去上面三個地方，Malaga 迫住經過 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n定係應該唔好咁貪心<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無乜機會會去到歐洲<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n覺得一日Madrid 太chur。起碼有兩個博物館Prado 同Reina Sofia 值得去，仲有皇宮要去。而皇宮同兩個博物館分別位於馬德里市中心嘅東西面。<br />\n不過你兩日day trip 返馬德里大約五六點，都會有啲時間去吓博物館，冇記錯d博物館有時夜晚仲會免費，慳返十幾蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a6d35b641b54b2958ecbf3e2b5fb9241da6b611","tid":25594,"uid":8934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T13:56:32.000Z","msg":"不過都係睇你同你女朋友鍾唔鍾意行博物館啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9490e13eddf7d46cf9d9cc3ca1a6b4d1f88d2294","tid":25594,"uid":57774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T13:55:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>不過都係睇你同你女朋友鍾唔鍾意行博物館啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n未必岩博物館 鍾意睇景多 btw Thanks <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31fe54c8f0eb29872d70270872e842eb7f0dae3a","tid":25594,"uid":57774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T03:27:20.000Z","msg":"問下先<br />\n有無巴絲去左mijas/Ronda?"},{"pid":"2ffac774acb7952d55bead79ab8b74121e96ff09","tid":25594,"uid":57774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T12:27:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}